data.description: Beautiful 2-story home located on the corner of Public and East Grand, just a couple blocks from Northern Oklahoma College! This spacious and modern home offers 2623 sq ft and the property expands over almost 6 LOTS! Spacious 4 bedrooms all with large closets, 2 full baths, 2 living areas (Master bedroom, additional living and second bath are located on second story).  Spacious and open kitchen/dining perfect for family gatherings and those that like to entertain with a fireplace in the family room.
